relation: Remember not to try and overdo it out there. However, if you do, and Mom's really far away, you know the doctor always has your back. For a modest fee, of course.
Remember to chant 'blue, blue" every night before bed, or this guy will find out. He will cut you!
Remember, no matter how unnecessary it looks, always wear the wrist strap.
